author: Rob Bolton
title: 2016-17 Web.com Tour graduate reshuffle
text:
2016-17 Web.com Tour graduate reshuffle January 30, 2017 By Rob Bolton , PGATOUR.COM Follow @RobBoltonGolf Twenty-five Web.com Tour members earned TOUR cards via the Regular Season with 25 more securing TOUR status via the Finals. (Steve Dykes/Getty Images) 
Reshuffles to occur at the conclusion of these tournaments • The RSM Classic (Nov. 20) • Genesis Open (Feb. 19) • Shell Houston Open (April 2) • Wells Fargo Championship (May 7) • FedEx St. Jude Classic (June 11) • John Deere Classic (July 16) 
NOTE: The following winners have been removed: Cody Gribble (Sanderson Farms Championship), Rod Pampling (Shriners Hospitals for Children Open), Mackenzie Hughes (The RSM Classic). 
Gain/Loss reflects movement if next reshuffle occurred at the conclusion of the last tournament. 
* - In the field at the Waste Management Phoenix Open as of Jan. 29. # - Top-10 alternate at the Waste Management Phoenix Open as of Jan. 29. Rank
